title: Return to the Nineteen Ninety Three
overview: Lin Xiaofan, an upstart in the modern business world, was killed by his business rival Chen Yuan, but he was unexpectedly reborn and traveled back to 1993. After time-traveling, Lin Xiaofan, his wife Jiang Yan and his boss Hong Yan started from scratch and started a new business. In the end, they completed the choice and self-growth in that golden age full of opportunities, and became a generation of wealth legends.
